		"description": "<p><em><strong>Association:</strong> Berserker class</em></p>\n<p>You still your hot-blooded fury and strike your enemy with icy, malicious calm.</p>\n<p>The next time you hit with a melee weapon attack while the spell is active, it deals an additional 3d6 cold damage. The target must also make a Constitution saving throw against your spell save DC or have its movement speed halved for 1 minute. The spell then ends.</p>\n<p>The creature may re-attempt the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on a success. Additionally, if the creature takes any fire damage, the effect ends early.</p>\n<p>You cannot cast this spell while raging even if you normally could due to archetype features or feat benefits.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
